        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36741269/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36741269/" class="">楚攻雍氏</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Ryuno/" class=" " title="Anthea.Xinci">Anthea.Xinci</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="36741269">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">楚攻雍氏，周粻秦、韩。楚王怒周，周之君患之。为周谓楚王曰：“以王之强而怒周，周恐，必以国合于所与粟之国，则是劲王之敌也，故王不如速解周恐。彼前的最而后得解，必厚事王矣。”</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-12-10 16:57</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                楚攻雍氏，周粻秦、韩。楚王怒周，周之君患之。为周谓楚王曰：“以王之强而怒周，周恐，必以国合于所与粟之国，则是劲王之敌也，故王不如速解周恐。彼前的最而后得解，必厚事王矣。”
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
